<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 12. Known distribution records of new leptonetid species from Korea 1 Falcileptoneta dolsan sp. nov. 2 Falcileptoneta naejangsan sp. nov. 3 Longileptoneta buyongsan sp. nov. 4 Longileptoneta byeonsanbando sp. nov. 5 Longileptoneta jirisan sp. nov." , "Figure 4. Falcileptoneta naejangsan sp. nov., female paratype A habitus, dorsal view B habitus, ventral view C internal genitalia, dorsal view. Abbreviations: At atrium SH spermathecae SS spermathecae stalk. Scale bars: equal for A, B." , "Figure 3. Falcileptoneta naejangsan sp. nov., holotype male A habitus, dorsal view B palpal bulb, ventral view C palp, prolateral view D palp, retrolateral view. Abbreviations: E embolus MS median sclerite PS prolateral sclerite. Scale bars: equal for C, D." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/496801" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/496793" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/496792" .

